Params: {2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Yes, at least we can feed ourselves if we work every day... No more unnecessary risks...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "But... Lucia, you've been coming back later and later...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "After this, Luna, we'll have all the time in the world to be together.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Little Girl', 3: "Luna, your sister is amazing! She's doing so much work."}
{2: 'Little Girl', 3: "And she looks after everyone as well. It's like she's the class monitor back in my school."}
{2: 'Little Boy', 3: 'Um... Can you... spare us some food...?'}
{2: 'Little Boy', 3: "It's so cold lately, we're all too sick to even work... We don't have food either... We're not going to live..."}
{2: 'Little Boy', 3: "I'm just borrowing it, okay? When I get my strength back, I can earn more food and return it to you, how's that?"}
{2: 'Little Girl', 3: "We live in a group, so we should help each other to better everyone's lives!"}
